%^YELLOW%^Skill: Athletics

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's athletics skill indicates their aptitude at various physical activities requiring speed, precision and/or reflexes. It would cover areas of jumping, climbing, rolling, and horseback abilities.

